        log.info("Saving task {}", t);
    }
}
Here, log is SLF4Jâ€™s API, but it delegates to Logback under the hood.

So if you want features like:

File logging

Rotation by date or size

Separate logs for error/info/debug

Archiving old logs

ğŸ’£ That logic must be done using Logback or another logging backend.

